name: I3ergsteiger
summary: Click, drag, launch! Explore Austrian's mountains with your trusty pickaxes and collect flowers and coins on the way to the top. Do you have what it takes to reach the peak?

name: I <3 You!
summary: Hello, stranger! Whoever you are, I do not care – I made this game for myself. Cassiopea is an AI that is created by me. She does not know a single thing about this world; you are free to teach her anything, and the outcome will be the direct result of your personal qualities. It’s easy to know a man by looking at how they deal with someone who can’t fight back. Good luck.
